snippet.title: ODR Hockey Heroes (KickstarterTrailer)
snippet.description:
ODR Hockey Heroes is a brand new arcade hockey video game featuring ultra-smooth pick-up-and-play controls that'll have you scoring goals and laying hitz like a true legend of the pond.



Back ODR Hockey Heroes on Kickstarter to bring back the fun to sports games!!


https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/odrhockeyheroes/odr-hockey-heroes?ref=ksrtwitter-prelaunch
